imdb.plot outline: Tune in to Cosmopolitan.com/love-is-on to watch LOVE STARTS NOW, an 8-episode series where Revlon and Cosmo give 8 deserving women the look, the advice and the confidence they need to get ready for love! In each episode, Kristin Cavallari and her glam squad will give a woman a beauty makeover and set her up on a blind date! Will it be love at first sight? Watch and find out.
